January 2020, gives California consumers enhanced rights with respect to their personal information that is collected by businesses. First, California consumers may opt out of having their personal information sold to other persons or parties. Second, they have a right to know:
1. What specific pieces of information a business has about the consumer;
2. Categories of personal information it has collected about the consumer;
3. Categories of sources from which the personal information is collecte...

